      "_id": "UjAFeXqOeuMwswPR",
      "name": "Cataclysmic Event (Recharge 4-6)",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The cataclysm cre- ates one of the following effects at random (roll 1d4): 1: Clinging Flames. Destreza Teste de Resistência: DC 23, cada criatura in a 60-foot-radius Sphere centered on a point the cataclysm can see within 150 feet. Falha: 45 (l 3d6) Fogo de dano. Sucesso: Metade do dano. Falha ou Sucesso: The target starts burning. 2: Freezing Waves. Força Teste de Resistência: DC 23, cada criatura in a 90-foot Cone. Falha: 22 (Sd8) Blud- geoning de dano plus 22 (Sd8) Frio de dano, and o alvo has the Caído condition. Sucesso: Metade do dano only. Falha ou Sucesso: The target's Speed is reduced to O until the end of its next turn . 3: Raging Storm. A storm cloud fills a 60-foot-radius Sphere centered on a point the cataclysm can see within 150 feet. The cloud lasts for 1 minute or until the cataclysm uses Cataclysmic Event again. Creatures entirely in the cloud have the Cego and Surdo conditions and can't cast spells with a Ver- bal component. Destreza Teste de Resistência: DC 23, cada criatura that enters the cloud for the first time on a turn or starts its turn there. Falha: 18 (4d8) Light- ning de dano plus 18 (4d8) Trovejante de dano. Sucesso: Metade do dano. 4: Swallowing Earth. Força Teste de Resistência: DC 23, cada criatura in a 90-foot Cube originating from a point on the ground within 150 feet. Falha: 18 (4d8) Concussão de dano plus 18 (4d8) Ácido de dano, and o alvo has the Caído condition and is buried under rubble. A buried target has the Impedido condition, has Total Cover, and is suffocating. As an action, a buried creature or another creature within 5 feet of it can make a DC 18 Força (Athletics) check. On a successful check, the creature is no lon- ger buried. Sucesso: Metade do dano only.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
